( q2* )

  \ Credit:
  \
  \ Original code by Wil Baden, published on Forth Dimensions
  \ 18/5 p. 29 (1997-01).

need d2*

: q2* ( n . . . -- 2n . . . )
  d2* >r >r  dup 0< if    d2* r> 1+ r>
                    else  d2* r> r>  then ;

( q+ q- q0< q0= qu< qnegate qabs )

